snippet.title: Double Dragon (Zeebo Remake) -  Full Game Longplay Walkthrough (Infuse)
snippet.description:
Full longplay / playthrough of the Zeebo remake of Double Dragon, developed by Brizo Interactive for the obscure brazilian console Zeebo and released only in Brazil and Mexico in 2009. Played on the newly released Zeebo emulator Infuse by Tuxality (http://tuxality.net/projects/infuse_zeebo_emulator).
Support the channel: https://ko-fi.com/neogamer
https://www.patreon.com/neogamertvga
